0]Amam2haruna[/uid] (2026-06-17 10:49):[/b]<br/><br/>说起来狼大早上发呆时间的时候会看世界杯吗[/quote]<br/>我不看足球", "lou": 3281, "content_length": 15, "reply_to": 872000902, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781664712}, {"pid": 872001720, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 110, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 10:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[b]Reply to [pid=872001379,45974302,7462]Reply[/pid] Post by [uid=38269023]绯瑚mzh[/uid] (2026-06-17 10:52)[/b]<br/>你们都不知道我之前也是做过 喝酒吃药的 <br/>甚至很强<br/>当年没有人比我更了解白酒", "lou": 3282, "content_length": 98, "reply_to": 872001379, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781664861}, {"pid": 872003301, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 62, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 11:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872002665,45974302,7464]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67097689]w木隐林[/uid] (2026-06-17 10:59):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，白酒也有上下游，设备材料涨价传导，国外映射这种东西吗[s:ac:哭笑]我贫瘠的想象力想象不出来白酒这东西有什么门道，可以侃侃门道吗，反正大家也不可能炒白水[/quote]<br/>他不一样  白酒是品牌映射 区域加成 和当地的利益输送等等<br/>然后那些边缘小票就不断的有各种功效酒出来加成<br/>炒股而已 有吹就能挣钱。", "lou": 3283, "content_length": 121, "reply_to": 872002665, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781665409}, {"pid": 872003877, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 130, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 11:06", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872002761,45974302,7464]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38269023]绯瑚mzh[/uid] (2026-06-17 11:00):[/b]<br/><br/>进大时代晚了，以前都是自己的号自己乱玩[s:a2:大哭] 。<br/>进来发现有人指导方向和技术还提示风险，甚至开车，是多无私伟大的人，真的非常感谢。[/quote]<br/>噢 我以前被喷是谜语人[s:ac:哭笑]<br/>不过后来我发现了  就和当时的热梗一样<br/>人再蠢还能学不会微积分吗？---------疑似钱学森说<br/><br/>那个时候我就懂了  <br/>只是我说的他们不理解而已 是我的表达可能不对<br/>那我用更浅显的语言看看能不能说通", "lou": 3284, "content_length": 194, "reply_to": 872002761, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781665599}, {"pid": 872004305, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 128, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 11:08", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872003316,45974302,7465]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67138111]Altyport[/uid] (2026-06-17 11:03):[/b]<br/><br/>看到这句话的我，严肃把 sai 佬加入重点监测对象[/quote]<br/>很简单 你一定要尊重把产业链做到极致的人<br/>不然我为什么半导体要留着小图的看法", "lou": 3285, "content_length": 77, "reply_to": 872003316, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781665738}, {"pid": 872006102, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 61, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 11:18", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872004585,45974302,7467]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67204929]1one-[/uid] (2026-06-17 11:10):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大足球还是挺好看的 可以试着看一看<br/>尤其是现场的氛围<br/>只要去过一次现场就会想去看第二次[s:ac:羞][/quote]<br/>我以前经营过 不好的东西<br/>就是那种只看开球走一批  看完角球走一批 看完进球数走一批的那种<br/>我对足球的内幕了解得比你们可能多一点。", "lou": 3286, "content_length": 123, "reply_to": 872004585, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781666339}, {"pid": 872007179, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 48, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 11:24", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872006786,45974302,7470]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60252995]724298723[/uid] (2026-06-17 11:22):[/b]<br/><br/>开始降温科技了？怎么我看都是散户恐慌卖出多一点，是我的错觉吗？[/quote]<br/>。。。。这不是黄线跌更多吗。。。。。。。。。", "lou": 3287, "content_length": 49, "reply_to": 872006786, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781666698}, {"pid": 872007379, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 61, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 11:26", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872007204,45974302,7470]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42270883]yyricky！[/uid] (2026-06-17 11:25):[/b]<br/><br/>世界杯又要走一批[/quote]<br/>你说的走 应该不会是我理解那种走吧<br/>西班牙对佛得角那场堪称经典。", "lou": 3288, "content_length": 65, "reply_to": 872007204, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781666765}, {"pid": 872008203, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 65, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 11:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "截至上午收盘  3800多家待涨", "lou": 3289, "content_length": 24, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781667050}, {"pid": 872010552, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 63, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 11:44", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872010162,45974302,7474]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=41179166]Lyssssss[/uid] (2026-06-17 11:42):[/b]<br/><br/>观察到大时代老登和小登的矛盾愈演愈烈，是老登最后的反抽吗[s:ac:偷笑][/quote]<br/>老登的是思想 不是股票<br/>思想的对立 是从古至今都有的", "lou": 3290, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 872010162, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781667895}, {"pid": 872016756, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 12:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872014395,45974302,7477]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=16690696]艾莉大爱啊[/uid] (2026-06-17 12:12):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:哭笑]上午11点那会算日内低点么狼大[/quote]<br/>哪有低点。你科技跌了？", "lou": 3291, "content_length": 27, "reply_to": 872014395, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781670635}, {"pid": 872017214, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 80, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 12:34", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=872016972,45974302,7478]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38140916]huohuo277[/uid] (2026-06-17 12:32):[/b]<br/><br/>冲高回落算不算跌[s:a2:doge][/quote]<br/>你们甚至想吃到上涨过程的回落波动？<br/>属实有点无敌了", "lou": 3292, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 872016972, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781670867}, {"pid": 872018764, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 162, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 12:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "小剧场基本到了  科技还在新高 低位还在新低的阶段了<br/>接下来非科技会逐渐调出来  胆子大的买所谓的低位科技  胆子一般的买指数ETF和科技ETF  胆子小的把个股切了买那种有点漂移的科技公墓<br/>这些就是科技的增量资金来了<br/><br/>所以接下来 我只考虑  <br/><br/>什么时候<br/><br/>卖<br/><br/>这个事。<br/><br/>当然不是现在。", "lou": 3293, "content_length": 240, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781671640}, {"pid": 872019838, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 58, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 12:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "反正你们到时候别说  啊？加速过了？我怎么没感觉？ 就行", "lou": 3294, "content_length": 50, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781672223}, {"pid": 872021361, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 63, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 13:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "黄线还在砸。非科技崩溃得比科技还快。", "lou": 3295, "content_length": 36, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781673009}, {"pid": 872022111, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 96, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 13:16", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "刚才那个要吃半导体ETF日内回落波动的  现在看看  是不是觉得自己很白痴？", "lou": 3296, "content_length": 65, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781673412}, {"pid": 872024144, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 141, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 13:34", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们前面还觉得我增加科技仓位的时候不是最好时机吗[s:ac:哭笑]<br/>你们也懂炒股？", "lou": 3297, "content_length": 60, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781674466}, {"pid": 872024759, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 131, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-17 13:39", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "170要+7了  你们懂我精选的含精量吗？", "lou": 3298, "content_length": 33, "14": {"13": 3}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1781674781}, {"pid": 872025110, "fid": 706, "tid